    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Community Moderation Assistant\\n\",\"**NLP Project 76 of 100** — Prioritize risky or toxic posts for human moderator review.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Synthetic moderation queue\\nposts = [\\n    ('Great discussion everyone!','safe'),('This is really helpful','safe'),\\n    ('You are an idiot for thinking this','toxic'),('Shut up nobody asked','toxic'),\\n    ('Interesting perspective, thanks','safe'),('I disagree but respect your view','safe'),\\n    ('This person should be banned','risky'),('Your argument is garbage','toxic'),\\n    ('Can someone explain further?','safe'),('STOP POSTING THIS SPAM','risky'),\\n    ('Amazing content as always','safe'),('Go away troll','risky'),\\n] * 20\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(posts, columns=['text','risk_level'])\\ndf = df.sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\n\\n# Priority score: toxic > risky > safe\\npriority_map = {'safe': 0, 'risky': 1, 'toxic': 2}\\ndf['priority'] = df['risk_level'].map(priority_map)\\n\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=3000)\\nX = tfidf.fit_transform(df['text'])\\nlr = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED)\\nlr.fit(X, df['priority'])\\ndf['predicted_priority'] = lr.predict(X)\\ndf['priority_label'] = df['predicted_priority'].map({0:'✅ Safe', 1:'⚠️ Risky', 2:'🚨 Toxic'})\\n\\nprint('Moderation Queue (sorted by priority):')\\nfor _, row in df.sort_values('predicted_priority', ascending=False).head(10).iterrows():\\n    print(f'  {row[\\\"priority_label\\\"]} | {row[\\\"text\\\"]}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Automated prioritization saves moderator time** by surfacing toxic content first.\\n\",\"- **Three-tier system (safe/risky/toxic)** enables graduated response.\\n\",\"- **For production, combine with user reputation scores** and content history.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
